com.interpss.core.net
Interface Bus

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
AclfBus, AclfBusChildNetRef, AcscBus, com.interpss.dist.DistBus, DistBusChildNetRef
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfBusChildNetRefImpl, AclfBusImpl, AcscBusImpl, BusImpl, DistBusChildNetRefImpl, com.interpss.dist.impl.DistBusImpl
public interface Bus
extends ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel

A representation of the model object 'Bus'. Bus class for representing a Bus concept for power system simulation. The bus may have multiple sections, which are stored in the busSecList.

The following features are supported:

  • Base Voltage
  • Sec No
  • Parent
  • Network
  • To Branch List
  • From Branch List
  • Bus Sec List

See Also:
NetPackage.getBus()
